comments: Tatum (BOS) hooks Morris Sr.'s (LAC) arm and immediately releases it as he dribbles up the floor.
George (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Tatum (BOS) during his dribble.
Smart (BOS) moves into George's (LAC) left arm, which is slightly extended, and the contact is marginal.
Smart (BOS) moves into Morris Sr.'s (LAC) space and initiates leg contact that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Powell (LAC) reaches in and incidental hand on ball contact occurs with Smart (BOS) as he rips through.
Replay review of the foul called on Powell (LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Powell (LAC) holds Smart's (BOS) arm, affecting his ability to pursue the loose ball.
Leonard (LAC) goes to, not through, Smart's (BOS) space and marginal contact occurs as he releases away during the drive.
Morris Sr. (LAC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Tatum (BOS) extends his leg and creates the contact with Kennard (LAC) during the jump shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) moves alongside George's (LAC) path and maintains a legal guarding position as marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Kennard (LAC) places an arm against Tatum (BOS) during his shot attempt but the contact is marginal.
George (LAC) initiates contact with Brown's (BOS) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Leonard (LAC) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
